column5: Happy Thanksgiving from Eddie North's to all our American friends.
Thanks for your wishing us Yanks a Happy Thanksgiving! Best wishes for you and your family!
Family, Friends, Fish and our neighbors to the north. We all have much to be thankful for. Matt
Thank you. Happy Holidays to you and your family!!!
Thanks Eddie, We'll save you a leg...Driving the ice this year?
Hi Joe,i will be outwest in January driving,love that job.
